{
  "stem": "16214.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "One time I recall when I was probably seven years old or so, one-- one of the people got really drunk, one of our neighbors.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "Because our brownstone, we could not occupy just by ourselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "We had to, under the Communists, you know, you just couldn't have more than two big rooms or something like that per family.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And we had to relinquish the rest of the building for other people to live in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And as a result, we had some neighbors that were drunk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And one of them got very drunk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And he said-- he started screaming one night, if the Germans didn't kill you, I will finish you Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And I remember my mother was terrified.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "She put me, sort of hid me under a bed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And the guy was just chopping at the door with a huge hammer, and-- and not a knife, it's sort of what you use in a forest, you know.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "I forget the name of the instrument.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "But he was just chopping the door down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And I really was terrified.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "Lucky my father was outside at the time, and he realized what was happening.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "So he ran to the police, and brought in the police who stopped him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "But the door was almost gone by the time the police came.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "So it was a horrifying moment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It wasn't easy for me, really, to get to appreciate or like Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After all, I was discriminated because my parents were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as a child, you-- you can't really think these things out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One time I recall, which it's very embarrassing for me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I think it's something worthwhile telling you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother was at a time with-- delivering my sister in Kutno.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
